data.text:
June 10, 1961 was a Saturday and it was the 161st day of the year 1961 in the Gregorian calendar.

June 10, 1961 can also be written as 6/10/1961 in the US and as 10/6/1961 in UK and Europe.

The Zodiac and Astrological sign for June 10th is Gemini.

Gemini is the 3rd sign in the Western Zodiac. People born between May 21st and June 20th belong to the Gemini sign: discover Gemini personality and who should a Gemini marry.

Babies born in June are either Gemini or Cancer. People born before June 20th are Gemini, while people born from June 21st have the sign of Cancer.

Moon phase

The moon phase on June 10, 1961 was Waning crescent.

The moon phase refers to the appearance of the Moon in the night sky on June 10, 1961 and is determined by the portion of the Moon's illuminated surface that is visible from Earth.

An observer located in New York City on June 10, 1961 at 10pm, would see the moon, being 1% full, rising at 03:57 am and setting at 06:53 pm.

The previous full moon was on May 30, 1961 while the next full moon would come on Jun 28, 1961.
